- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on restyling GUIs for end-users and app developers. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel neural style transfer model for image processing. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper uses a neural network for style transfer. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is relevant as the paper deals with restyling graphical assets of apps. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with image processing and style transfer.
